{"tid":2016301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"理大衝突再多12名男女被控參與暴動罪　下周一東區法院提堂","createTime":"2020-05-14T09:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T11:01:30.000Z","uid":124630,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2c281f851104de6b3766ef4fced406ccc13d7fc9","tid":2016301,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"去年11月香港理工大學爆發激烈衝突，警方於11月18日清場時拘捕13男2女，年齡介乎16至61歲，當中8男2女其後拒保候查，獲暫時釋放，另外5名男子則繼續保釋候查。警方表示經進一步調查及徵詢法律意見後，今日（14日）在全港各區共拘捕5男2女，連同該5名獲保釋男子，警方暫時共起訴該12名年齡介乎18至60歲的男女一項「參與暴動」罪，其中3人另加控一項「管有工具可作非法用途」罪，1人另加控一項「在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器」罪。案件將於5月18日上午在東區裁判法院提堂。警方指拘捕行動仍在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n心情好複雜，大家喺度揾口罩抗疫嘅同時，班曱甴冇停過手，希望大家行動小心，耐冇大掃除嘅執下屋，留意下有冇陌生人跟蹤自己，將被捕風險減到最低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource01唔貼link了"},{"pid":"7a84025bcd197224f72ec6ecf17a7860aba11a73","tid":2016301,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821b9ae09476a726d98c2b3d66a80b5539a3e9b5","tid":2016301,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:45:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://legcopetition.wixsite.com/form\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegcopetition.wixsite.com%2Fform&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7l8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=262c126f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legcopetition.wixsite.com/form</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立法會三不投聯署</span></span></strong> 就黎deadline啦<br />\n大家簽完記得share埋俾你地身邊既同路人呀"},{"pid":"851bcf9fb06725dc8cdbe2e18680b7add098a03a","tid":2016301,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:46:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7ce90f4c8bec141b31570f263c85f057ca58fc3a","tid":2016301,"uid":124630,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"希望大家有時間做下旁聽師